question.title: Missing app jar files in contents directory of Widlfly 31 VFS deployment location
question.body:
We are migrating from Wildfly 30.0.1.FINAL to 31.0.1.FINAL.

In 30.0.1.FINAL all the application libraries were copied to %wildfly-31.0.1.Final%\standalone\tmp\vfs\deployment\deployment90110bdf73e52ecf\contact.jar-c26da1d272c45e0d on start of the server.

But in 31.0.1.FINAL it just creates a empty folder inside %wildfly-31.0.1.Final%\standalone\tmp\vfs\deployment\deployment90110bdf73e52ecf\contact.jar-6fa846a7d1d310c5\contents

JDK used is openjdk-17.0.2. Unfortunatley i couldn't see any error in server log also.
